<h1>Cliche Finder</h1>

<p>It&#8217;s not an essay, but I hope I can count it as a blog post. Here&#8217;s a new hack I made for my friend Quinn:</p>

<p><a href="http://cliche.theinfo.org/">Cliche Finder</a></p>


<p><i>You should follow me on twitter <a href="http://twitter.com/aaronsw">here</a>.</i></p>
<p class="posted">December 22, 2006</p>

